headline: Delta flight returns to Boston after takeoff over 'smoky odor' detected on board
summary: A Delta Air Lines flight from Boston to New Orleans had to return to Logan International Airport shortly after takeoff on Sunday over a smoky odor detected onboard.Delta Flight 1398 departed Boston...
